<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THERE'S A FRIEND FOR LITTLE CHILDREN</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Naupangte din guolpha a um,
 I chung thangvan akhun;
 Danglam ngeilo Guol pha chuh,
 A hehpih dai ngeilo;
 Amah chu leisiet guolte,
 Kidang zel bang ei puoi;
 Zie guol hin A put min lul,
 Hi pu tak mawng ahi.

[V2]
 2. Naupangte din kichawlhdamna,
 Chung thangvan ah a um;
 Pathien hehpih naupang te'n,
 &quot;He pa&quot; ti'n a sam ui;
 Buoina cheng apat chawlhna,
 Gitloh, lauhna beita;
 Ziechun Kristien naupangte,
 Kumsawt in chawl ta'n au.

[V3]
 3. Naupangte din In a um hi,
 I chung thangvan akhun;
 Ziechun, muonna Isun vai A hawm,
 Kipah, muonna In ah;
 Van In bang lei ah umlo,
 Tehpih ding le um lo;
 Micheng chu a kipak ui,
 Mun nuomzaw dang umlo.

[V4]
 4. Naupangte din lukhuk a um,
 I chung thangvan akhun;
 Kuole Isu lam en chun,
 Dantak leh hun khu'n au;
 Lallukhuk vam lopi chu,
 A deihguol bawlte leh;
 Leia A min hehpihte,
 Cheng chu Aman pie'n a.

[V5]
 5. Naupangte lasak ding a um,
 I chung thangvan akhun;
 Kisa zing zing mahlele,
 Chul thei ngei talo ding;
 Angelte nasan inle,
 A sak ngei loh uh la;
 Hukdampa'n helo mahleu,
 Lal bangin a ho ui.

[V6]
 6. Naupangte din puon lopi um,
 I chung thangvan akhun;
 Kingkang gihawih pen a um,
 Zawhna tumbak a um;
 A bawnin chunglam ah um,
 Krista mai a muh ding;
 Hungun, naupang deihum te,
 Ziehaw chu chang dingin.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>411</hymn_number>
</song>